{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"starts-with","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/starts-with","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>starts-with</code> 関数は第 1 引数の文字列が第 2 引数の文字列で始まるかどうかを調べ、true または false を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">starts-with(<em>haystack</em>, <em>needle</em>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"haystack\"><em><code>haystack</code></em></dt>\n <dd>検索される文字列。</dd>\n <dt id=\"needle\"><em><code>needle</code></em></dt>\n <dd>検索する文字列。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em><code>haystack</code></em>が<em><code>needle</code></em> で始まれば <code>true</code>。 そうでなければ <code>false</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-starts-with\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko での対応","isH3":true,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"starts-with 関数は第 1 引数の文字列が第 2 引数の文字列で始まるかどうかを調べ、true または false を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"starts-with","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"starts-with","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":